{"tid":21443,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲男陽具兩度被蜘蛛咬","createTime":"2016-12-03T23:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:32:33.000Z","uid":12709,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edf1cc35363d6e50f80c9b135fad77533a3b1aa5","tid":21443,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:17:11.000Z","msg":"澳洲大陸真的充滿毒物與危險動物嗎？一名不幸男子陽具連兩次被毒蜘蛛咬，距離上次意外還不到半年。英國廣播公司報導，21歲男子喬丹（Jordan）昨天在雪梨使用一個移動廁所時，忽然感到下體一陣刺痛，與上次被螫咬感覺相同。男子受訪表示「當時我覺得自己是全澳洲最衰的人了，我坐在馬桶上，感到一陣刺痛，那種感覺跟上次一樣，我心想『天哪竟然又被咬一次，怎麼可能？』」。喬丹說這次他不清楚咬他的蜘蛛種類，被同事送到附近醫院後已經康復，「我第一次被咬他們很擔心，但這次他們就開始笑我了」。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"bf550097ecc92ce2b6e78ea5efeb61562971b3a8","tid":21443,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56f9c673769c339ef6ac2a1c209269fd3671a24","tid":21443,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:43:35.000Z","msg":"慘過比蜘蛛咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb16cd2a4187f989e2ceedd69a319ae479051f8","tid":21443,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🕷️"},{"pid":"7ab4ab1070b12c91feb0d2d5e2817182c15f8fdc","tid":21443,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:50:48.000Z","msg":"正宗毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5c5e1401d13e3010547f2bc11cca01083ae11e","tid":21443,"uid":30638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:56:25.000Z","msg":"下體射出白色物質，蜘蛛俠"},{"pid":"940e5304d9d9fdd9d7f188a72c3a28fd2f73b0f9","tid":21443,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:57:29.